B.D7=new A.cY("What are the delivery times?","Standard delivery is within 24\u201348 hours after order confirmation. For same-day delivery, orders must be placed before 10 AM on available days.")
B.D8=new A.cY("Do you deliver to my area?","Coverage is expanding constantly. Enter your address at checkout \u2014 the app will confirm if your area is currently served.")
B.D2=new A.cY("Can I schedule delivery for a specific date?","Scheduled delivery windows are available for select areas. If available in your region, a calendar selector will appear at checkout.")
B.Fw=s([B.D7,B.D8,B.D2],t.bw)
B.KA=new A.m6(B.n1,B.Fw,"Delivery")
B.Dd=new A.cY("Are the products really organic?","Products marked with the organic badge are certified by our partner farmers. Each product page shows the farm name, certifications, and harvest practices.")
B.D4=new A.cY("What if a product is out of stock?","Stock is updated in real time. If a product runs out, it will be shown as unavailable. You can add it to your watchlist and be notified when it's back.")
B.D3=new A.cY("What do the units mean (kg, unit, bunch)?",'Each product shows its unit of measure on the detail page. For example, "1 kg" means you\'ll receive approximately 1 kilogram, and "1 bunch" means a standard bunch as picked by the farmer.')
B.F7=s([B.Dd,B.D4,B.D3],t.bw)
B.Kz=new A.m6(B.fJ,B.F7,"Products")
B.DD=new A.d_(983127,"MaterialIcons",null,!1)
B.D9=new A.cY("What payment methods are accepted?","Harvest currently supports credit card, debit card, and digital wallets. Payment is processed securely at checkout.")
B.Df=new A.cY("Is my payment information safe?","All payment data is encrypted end-to-end. We never store your full card number. Transactions are protected by industry-standard PCI DSS compliance.")
B.De=new A.cY("How do refunds work?","Refunds for cancelled orders are processed within 3\u20135 business days back to your original payment method. For quality issues, contact us within 24 hours of delivery.")
